# Normalise line endings to LF in the repo on every platform.
# Text files are detected by Git, then stored with LF and checked out as-is.
# Without this, Windows' core.autocrlf=true checks files out as CRLF and
# `bun run lint:fix` (biome, configured to LF) rewrites them on every save —
# producing endless phantom diffs.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Keep binary assets byte-identical.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.eot binary
*.zip binary
*.tar binary
*.tar.gz binary
*.tgz binary
*.lockb binary
